{"tid":2070495,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"日本禁映了37年的電影, 下月解禁上映","createTime":"2020-06-19T07:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T08:28:11.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6681219dc8f10a00b50d9d482d7184c84fc2ada7","tid":2070495,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"2020-06-01<br />\n多國禁播心理驚悚片《Angst》，日本電影院解封震撼上架<br />\n<br />\n奧地利電影《Angst》故事建立在八十年代一個真實殺人事件之上，以殺人犯的角度講述連環兇殺的故事。被分類成 psychothriller 的《Angst》當年在維也納上映後受到極大爭議，隨後因為內容太震撼而德國和英國等地陸續被禁播。後來電影在法國以錄影帶方式得以發行，並在後續成為名聲超高的 cult 片。日本最近買來播放版權（被評為 R15+ 級別），<strong>將在 7 月 3 日解封這個被困住超過 37 年的恐怖片，讓它重見天日。</strong><br />\n<br />\n這可以說是電影導演 Gerald Kargl 的舉世 one hit wonder 代表作。1983 年拍成的《Angst》（焦慮／恐懼）當年因為尺度問題而遇上很大的制肘，多國禁播的情況下令製作組損失慘重；而飾演男主角殺人狂魔 K 的奧地利演員 Erwin Leder 至今一直活躍影視行業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://iamsy.com/japan-july-angst-1983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiamsy.com%2Fjapan-july-angst-1983%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=917f8b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://iamsy.com/japan-july-angst-1983/</a>"},{"pid":"b9ca09ba27292edf2fa56d7e943e5d9ba19c4f4b","tid":2070495,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/StQiz2Ke_gM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FStQiz2Ke_gM&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=338aee97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/StQiz2Ke_gM</a>"},{"pid":"882895ec757026a89f1e5c29fa160c6f9b0d481b","tid":2070495,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"香港會唔會有得睇 講到咁吧炮"},{"pid":"d232384003e0c7a07ed57e799355e2be2c182300","tid":2070495,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"882895ec757026a89f1e5c29fa160c6f9b0d481b","tid":2070495,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:23:50.000Z","msg"